Package org.ejvm.inspection

Provides classes to inspect compiled eJVM bytecode.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EjvmProgram
    Represents a compiled eJVM program and offers methods to retrieve information about said program from its compiled form, e.g. the number of methods or constants.
    MethodInformation
    Encapsulates all information available about a method of an EjvmProgram.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidEjvmProgramException
